'''Nawaf Mashari Abdulrahman Boushal''' (born 16 September 1999) is a Saudi Arabian professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[right-back]] for [[Saudi Pro League]] club [[Al Nassr FC|Al-Nassr]] and the [[Saudi Arabia national football team|Saudi Arabia national team]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.kooora.com/?player=130297|title=اللاعب: نواف بوشل|website=Kooora|language=ar}}</ref>

==Career==
[[File:Nawaf Boushal - Persepolis vs Al Nassr, February 2025.jpg|thumb|Boushal with Al-Nassr in 2025]]
Boushal started his career at hometown club [[Al-Fateh SC|Al-Fateh]]. On 31 August 2019, he signed his first professional contract with the club.<ref>{{cite web |title=الفتح يوقّع عقدًا احترافيًا مع نواف البوشل لمدة 3 سنوات |url=https://slaati.com/2019/08/31/p1474932.html}}</ref> He made his debut on 22 November 2019 in the league match against [[Abha Club|Abha]].<ref>{{cite web |title=ABHA VS. AL FATEH 3 - 1 |url=https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2019/11/22/saudi-arabia/pro-league/abha/al-fath-alahsa/3102206/}}</ref> On 2 March 2022, Boushal renewed his contract with Al-Fateh.<ref>{{cite web |title=الفتح يمدد عقد "بوشل" لعامين إضافيين .. دون الكشف عن التفاصيل |url=https://sabq.org/sports/%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%81%D8%AA%D8%AD-%D9%8A%D9%85%D8%AF%D8%AF-%D8%B9%D9%82%D8%AF-%D8%A8%D9%88%D8%B4%D9%84-%D9%84%D8%B9%D8%A7%D9%85%D9%8A%D9%86-%D8%A5%D8%B6%D8%A7%D9%81%D9%8A%D9%8A%D9%86-%D8%AF%D9%88%D9%86-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%83%D8%B4%D9%81-%D8%B9%D9%86-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AA%D9%81%D8%A7%D8%B5%D9%8A%D9%84}}</ref> On 20 January 2023, Boushal joined [[Al-Nassr FC|Al-Nassr]] on a four-and-a-half-year deal.<ref>{{cite web |title=النصر يدعم صفوفه بنجم الفتح نواف بوشل |url=https://www.dawriplus.com/news/66292-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%86%D8%B5%D8%B1-%D9%8A%D8%AF%D8%B9%D9%85-%D8%B5%D9%81%D9%88%D9%81%D9%87-%D8%A8%D9%86%D8%AC%D9%85-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%81%D8%AA%D8%AD-%D9%86%D9%88%D8%A7%D9%81-%D8%A8%D9%88%D8%B4%D9%84.html}}</ref>

